Imogen Hinds, Ed.D., M.Ed.Assistant Vice Provost for Housing Operations and Stanford Conferences

            Stanford Neighborhoods          
Undergraduate housing is organized in neighborhoods, each offering a broad spectrum of living including dormitories, theme houses, coops, self-ops, Greek houses, and apartments.
 More










            Graduate Housing Lottery          
Graduate students are assigned housing in the annual Housing Lottery. Housing options are available for single students, couples and students with children.
